 Reviews # ) When I recalled Paolo&rsquo;s introduction about this position in the first interview, he emphasized on &ldquo;deep expertise in chemical characterization&rdquo;. I mentioned about the data analysis report a couple of times in the follow-up interview. I think I distracted (or left impression with) them with my data analysis.
) I could mention how my experience in GC/MS, HPLC, ICP-OES, DSC, and TGA could help them, such as design of experiment, ANOVA for method development, process/instrument optimization. my plan of building database of troubleshooting, faster data processing.
